name: Fix: 505 Error
body: - Fixed 505 Error in Google Play Store.

name: Starting Stretching
body:
- Added Rest Timer.
- Added Starting Stretching Routine.

- Fixes a bug where changing progression does not notify the app that this exercise is no longer needed to be completed (e.g. missed exercises section shows old progressions).
- Added bottom navigation and removed navigation drawer for better user experience.
- Added feedback section in Home.

- Added Molding Mobility, Flexibility Routine with Starting Stretching coming soon.
- Updated all videos to high quality MP4 videos done by Nick & Antranik.
- Explore your logged workouts with beautiful graphs and statistics.
- Added Home, a single place to switch between routines.
- Export your workouts to CSV file (all logged workouts option) - experimental.
- Improved "log reps" dialog with previous workout statistics.

- Fixed a bug where Workout Dialog is showing the logged workout for wrong date so it was impossible to see the previous workouts (all your data is safe, don't worry).
- Fixed a bug where toolbar exercise title does not change or action buttons disappear.

- Reps Logger.
- Kotlin Presenters with RxLifecycle.
- Updated RR.
- Removed Amazon Associates to hopefully fix Google Play compatibility issues.

- Kotlin.
- Add time automatically to logged workouts.
- Bug fixes.
- Multiple routines (turned off by default).

- Hold down buttons in Log Workout Dialog rather than click them to change the values (much faster and better UX).
- When creating new set in the same exercise, the values are copied from the previous set so it's much faster to log the reps.

- Log workouts.
- Buy equipment on Amazon US/UK.
- New navigation drawer (switch between menu and workout).
- Workout calendar.
- Progress activity with graphs.
- Store data using Realm.
- SD Card support.
- Bug fixes.
- New package name (com.bodyweight.fitness).
- Completely new release to the Play Store.
- [Free](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bodyweight.fitness.free)
- [Pro](https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bodyweight.fitness.pro)

name: 1.01 Release
body:
- New amazing icon! Thanks to @Ruben_Dantuma
- Pick exercises based on your level (icon in the toolbar shows up in relevant sections).
- Chosen exercises are remembered between sessions.
- Alarm sounds when timer goes off (based on the settings).
- Screen stays on when app is open (experimental feature, change in the settings).
- Link to the FAQ (/r/bodyweightfitness)
- Bug fixes!
